<comment>Initialize the project</comment>
<comment>======================</comment>

Switch to the new project and run <comment>ddev start</comment>.
Now install all Composer packages by running <comment>ddev composer update</comment>.
Run <comment>ddev config --auto</comment> to create the final DDEV configuration.

<comment>Add project packages</comment>
<comment>====================</comment>

Additional project packages should be added within the <comment>packages</comment> directory.
When requiring them via Composer, they get automatically linked to the target destinations.
